 r/p/s lite
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 This is an implementation of the rock paper scissors game utilizing the Bluetooth connectivity of
 android devices. One can play a game of rock paper scissors with a friend, relative, or co-worker
 in all out fun!

 Setup - 

 1. build this project in android studio
 2. attach two mobile devices
 3. run the project
 4. connect devices together with 'host' and 'join' buttons